Package: raudiomate
Title: Helper functions to generate audio from midifiles and play them
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Urs", "Wilke", , "urs.wilke@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Transform midi files to wav and mp3 and provide html tags to play them in rmarkdown html_documents.
